    "Cluster ID is the number of the cluster, the larger the cluster size, the smaller the number.",
    "size represents the number of members contained in the cluster, Silhouette is a measure of the homogeneity of the members of the whole cluster, the larger the value, the higher the similarity of the members of the cluster.",
